## Enable Controllers and Start Flow

### Profile

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **nipyapi Profile** | `{{ nipyapi_profile }}` |

### CLI Commands

```bash
# Enable all controller services
# Two Private Key Service controllers will fail — this is EXPECTED with SNOWFLAKE_MANAGED auth
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} canvas schedule_all_controllers "<process_group_id>" True

# Verify configuration
# Expected result: 29/31 passed
# The 2 failures are Forge Private Key Service and Snowflake Private Key Service — ignore them
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} ci verify_config "<process_group_id>"

# Start the flow
nipyapi --profile {{ nipyapi_profile }} canvas schedule_process_group "<process_group_id>" True
```

### Expected Timeline

Data will appear in `{{ dest_db | upper }}.{{ dest_schema | upper }}.{{ dest_table | upper }}` within approximately **10 minutes** after starting — one 5-minute fetch cycle followed by one 5-minute merge buffer flush.
